modName: Bar Rag in Clean and Grubby Versions
summary: A little retexture of the static bar rag that is found all around Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
This is just a simple retexture, look at the picture to see what you are getting. Obviously you can only have one or the other installed at the same time.

The 'clean' version comes with a new normal map, but the grubby one doesn't.

Pictures are taken with Relighting Skyrim, Enhanced Lighting for ENB and 'Seasons of Skyrim' ENB active.
